{"tid":1332760,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[反擊中聯辦5毛洗地] 成立一隊連登網軍，狂推有用文宣post上熱門","createTime":"2019-07-19T12:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-20T10:20:51.000Z","uid":209263,"like":67,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":41,"replies":[{"pid":"80c2b14ad239f6d436a1a9b7f507d844dd9e5e8d","tid":1332760,"uid":209263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:12:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">［自己論壇自己救］<br />\n<br />\n召集一隊網軍<br />\n<br />\n防止中聯辦五毛洗地<br />\n</span></span><br />\n請大家入<br />\nTg Channel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flihkgnetarmy%20&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMVyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7e7e4eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy </a><br />\n<br />\n現況：<br />\n<br />\n越來越多大眾市民，唔止係年青人，全部都用連登接收信息，但係好多人其實都係新手上路，唔識欣賞假膠，唔識分辨五毛。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">近呢一個星期出現大量分化、假消息、引導性標題Post，洗走有意思嘅討論同埋721嘅宣傳。</span><br />\n<br />\n此舉明顯為政府一洗太平地、控制輿論嘅手段，好多人已經多次呼籲，<span style=\"color: red;\">見到五毛Post就唔好回覆、負評上一頁。</span><br />\n<br />\n但係唔知點解，好多人都係忍唔到手，又或者頭50個回覆全部都係五毛，所以無奈下就會俾啲垃圾Post上晒熱門。<br />\n<br />\n解決方法：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">成立一條網軍Channel，以投票嘅方式決定推某特定議題嘅Post。</span><br />\n<br />\n請大家入<br />\nTg Channel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flihkgnetarmy%20&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMVyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7e7e4eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy </a><br />\n<br />\n力求達致以下三大成效：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">1. 宣傳有意思嘅post，將佢哋推上熱門</span><br />\n<br />\n例如721個post成日會朝早唔見咗，好需要大家嘅努力一齊推翻上去，依家政府擺到明就係好撚驚，所以一定要做好文宣。<br />\n<br />\n唔一定係特定議題，但係如果有人有一啲有意義嘅提議，經大家投票決定之後，都可以幫佢哋推上熱門。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n2. 解決引導性標題導致分化既post </span><br />\n<br />\n例如今朝楊岳橋講既野，明明係啱大家心水，但係就因為引導性標題，加埋一開始嘅五毛回覆，令大部份人錯撳負評。<br />\n<br />\n網軍可以用壓倒性正評，壓返轉頭，以正視聽。唔係話一定唔可以鬧泛民，希望大家係認清事實咁樣鬧，唔係標題黨，睇完標題同見負評多d就鬧。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">3. 洗走啲垃圾戇鳩講埋啲廢話嘅熱門post</span><br />\n<br />\n呢樣唔解釋了。睇下熱門幾多垃圾post.............而家又無曬721post<br />\n<br />\n請大家入 <br />\nTg Channel link: <a href=\"https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Flihkgnetarmy%20&d=iVbTvSvdcfz%2Fe2yCQDPMVyaGrLhPWbn%2F%2Bskqqi57m1s%3D&h=7e7e4eae\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/lihkgnetarmy </a><br />\n<br />\n總之，一句講曬<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">以彼之道還施彼身<br />\n<br />\n自己論壇自己救<br />\n<br />\n全力推爆721</span></span>"},{"pid":"7d16db626b254cade5d3478ff1d1914ded182bba","tid":1332760,"uid":209263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:12:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7700485639b6f768f8f8c5b4adcb549760f99ba","tid":1332760,"uid":255635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33c0ff8488b2bf72ba8f83cc5a38d64bffa4775f","tid":1332760,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:25.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"06f02dfc8ccef8ef2181ef60d07df474ee273fdd","tid":1332760,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:35.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"7ac8314feca673117cefa246e2bb6d8965d7ee71","tid":1332760,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:47.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"a4cfb24a50c956436ca0741943da580aef3a21c8","tid":1332760,"uid":132362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"33756294aa0f7af0aa9210440d43a5af08f3418e","tid":1332760,"uid":21742,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:13:57.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4d17cca06f5a7df30c2ac230a1f04a3355dc0540","tid":1332760,"uid":255635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T12:14:01.000Z","msg":"入左，推！！"},{"pid":"c33f7f61a24a45c2ab8e7dfa7463